NAME
	libepiterm - A library for creating epiterminals

DESCRIPTION
	This library provide the basics for creating epiterminals.

	Programs like tmux(1) and screen(1) are a type of
	epiterminals known as terminal multiplexers. Any
	pseudo-terminal run from inside another terminal is an
	epiterminals.

RATIONALE
	Creating an epiterminal is very much work. We need
	a library.

SEE ALSO
	posix_openpt(3), ptmx(4)

